               <p>
                  <milestone n="1" unit="line"/> Hermaphilos to Theodoros, greetings. I hereby send you a copy of the memorandum from Teos. 
If it is in the contract description, the work should be finished, so he will not cause us any trouble later, at the irrigation. 
<milestone n="5" unit="line"/> Farewell. Year 7, Epeiph 3. [Teos the ...] of Tanchoiris to Hermaphilos, greetings. [...] to Theodoros, the engineer. [...].
               </p>
            </div>
            <div n="v" type="textpart">
               <p>
                  <milestone n="9" unit="line"/> Year 7, Epeiph 3. Hermaphilos; copy of the memorandum from Teos, asking that the work be assigned to them. To Theodoros.
<note>Translation with slight modifications: B. Van Beek in P.Petr.Kleon, p. 87, © Peeters</note>
               </p>
